{"tid":1684151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家又忘記左我地點樣撐到今時今日","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T03:26:14.000Z","uid":44661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ada456557d7f2c9a40b56463a1afe1b8c03b689a","tid":1684151,"uid":44661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"係兄弟爬山,各有各做<br />\n和勇同心<br />\n不分化,不割蓆"},{"pid":"7bc1cb3f4af33e86e757307f0e7af197bd67238c","tid":1684151,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=b96ea552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf804d2beee9f505dfbfdee36cc068f96801b44","tid":1684151,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:26:14.000Z","msg":"不分和勇，大家都係革命義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1683656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1683656</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}